      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery to an 8,400 RPM redline. This driver-spec example is equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission and the Variable M Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. The suspension maintains its factory composure with functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and multi-link rear geometry. Recent service includes throttle actuator replacement and a comprehensive cooling system pressure test. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a crisp shift linkage. A performance-oriented chassis ready for spirited driving.",
